;","strongs_def":"Sheja, an Israelite","kjv_def":"Sheva (from the margin)."},"H7865":{"id":"H7865","lemma":"שִׂיאֹן","translit":"Sîyʼôn","pron":"see-ohn'","derivation":"from H7863 (שִׂיא); peak;","strongs_def":"Sion, the summit of Mount Hermon","kjv_def":"Sion.","pos":"proper noun with reference to a mountain","usage":"Sion(1x)"},"H7866":{"id":"H7866","lemma":"שִׁיאוֹן","translit":"Shîyʼôwn","pron":"shee-ohn'","derivation":"from the same as H7722 (שׁוֹא); ruin;","strongs_def":"Shijon, a place in Palestine","kjv_def":"Shihon.","pos":"proper locative noun","usage":"Shion(1x)"},"H7867":{"id":"H7867","lemma":"שִׂיב","translit":"sîyb","pron":"seeb","derivation":"a primitive root;","strongs_def":"properly, to become aged, i.e. (by implication) to grow gray","kjv_def":"(be) grayheaded.","pos":"verb","usage":"grayheaded(2x)"},"H7868":{"id":"H7868","lemma":"שִׂיב","translit":"sîyb","pron":"seeb","derivation":"(Aramaic) corresponding to H7867 (שִׂיב)","strongs_def":"{properly, to become aged, i.e. (by implication) to grow gray}","kjv_def":"elder.","pos":"verb","usage":"elder(5x)"},"H7869":{"id":"H7869","lemma":"שֵׂיב","translit":"sêyb","pron":"sabe","derivation":"from H7867 (שִׂיב);","strongs_def":"old age","kjv_def":"age."},"H7870":{"id":"H7870","lemma":"שִׁיבָה","translit":"shîybâh","pron":"shee-baw'","derivation":"by permutation from H7725 (שׁוּב);","strongs_def":"a return (of property)","kjv_def":"captivity.","pos":"masculine noun","usage":"captivity(1x)"},"H7871":{"id":"H7871","lemma":"שִׁיבָה","translit":"shîybâh","pron":"shee-baw'","derivation":"from H3427 (יָשַׁב);","strongs_def":"residence","kjv_def":"while...lay."},"H7872":{"id":"H7872","lemma":"שֵׂיבָה","translit":"sêybâh","pron":"say-baw'","derivation":"feminine of H7869 (שֵׂיב);","strongs_def":"old age","kjv_def":"(be) gray (grey hoar,-y) hairs (head,-ed), old age.","pos":"feminine noun","usage":"grayheaded(1x), hoary(1x)"},"H7873":{"id":"H7873","lemma":"שִׂיג","translit":"sîyg","pron":"seeg","derivation":"from H